[normal] N
[normal]either the government nor Royal Mail has specified how much 
[normal]capital is needed, when it is needed or what it is needed for
[normal]. Also, there is no 
[normal]indication that selling Royal Mail will result in any additional capital for the company. Any revenue from a sale will go to the Treasury not the company.
