[normal]The CWU announced the results of its consultative ballot of 112,000 members in Roy
[normal]al Mail on 19 June 2013. There was a 74% turnout and members answered as foll
[normal]ows to the four questions posed: d
[normal]o you oppose the privatisation of Royal Mail? 
[normal]YES 96%[bold]; 
[normal]d
[normal]o you support the boycott of competitors' mail? 
[normal]YES 92%[bold]; d
[normal]o you support the CWU Pay claim
[normal]? 
[normal]YES 99%[bold]; and d
[normal]o you support the policy of non-cooperation? 
[normal]YES 92%[bold].
